Lobo\u00a0Mau.details: Who'd have thought that the TzHaar could be terrorised by a malevolent armadillo? Through a little mining and lots of theatre, I completed my task.
I infiltrated the Prisoner of Walrus camp, rescued Larry and Teddy, did a rock show with Ping and Pong, and escaped in a submarine.
Lobo\u00a0Mau.text: Quest complete: Some Like It Cold

Lobo\u00a0Mau.details: I battled a dangerous abomination and avenged the death of V.
I killed 12 mithril dragons.
I killed 16 mithril dragons.
I killed 29 mithril dragons.
A new dagannoth mother threatened civilisation itself around the northern seas, but with a mighty force of Fremennik and their allies at my back, I have trapped her.
I escape Sliske's twisted game with the Barrows Brothers. Sadly Linza was turned into a wight in the process.
I helped the Gower brothers solve the mystery of the disappearing cabbages and repair the life altar Behind the Scenes.
Completing Haunted Mine has given me enough Quest Points to pass the 360 QP milestone.
Deep beneath Morytania, I dodged pickaxes, puzzled with minecarts and collected fungi. Not only that, but I defeated Treus and collected a salve shard!
I now have at least 14000000 experience points in the Woodcutting skill.
Balnea's entrepreneurial spirit turned Oo'glog into a successful holiday resort for weary adventurers, if you like mud...
Lobo\u00a0Mau.text: Quest complete: As A First Resort...

Lobo\u00a0Mau.details: I prevailed over Rabid Jack's minions in their most recent dastardly plot to destroy the world with Zombio-mechanical weaponry.
I now have at least 14000000 experience points in the Thieving skill.
I have rescued Hannibus from his stone prison and helped determine his future and the future of the Ilujanka.
Lobo\u00a0Mau.text: Quest complete: One of a Kind

Lobo\u00a0Mau.details: The bigger they are, the harder they fall! The giant has taken a fair old beating, and this grim tale has come to a rather satisfying end.
